Package org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.server

Interface JDBCBackendCfg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BackendCfg, Configuration, LocalBackendCfg, PluggableBackendCfg
    public interface JDBCBackendCfg
extends PluggableBackendCfg
    A server-side interface for querying JDBC Backend settings.

    A JDBC Backend stores application data in JDBC source.
